[[File:Spiritual ranger icon.png|left]]
'''Spiritual rangers''' are powerful [[Ranged]] [[Slayer monsters]] found in the [[God Wars Dungeon]]. There are five types of spiritual rangers: [[Saradomin]]ists, [[Zamorak]]ians, [[Bandos]]ians, [[Armadyl]]eans and [[Zaros]]ians. Spiritual rangers require 63 [[Slayer]] to kill, and the [[Troll Stronghold]] quest must be partially complete to gain access to the God Wars Dungeon. [[Spiritual creatures]] cannot be given as a [[Slayer task]] if the player has not completed the [[Death Plateau]] quest.

