==Trivia==
* When Spiritual rangers are fighting other monsters, they seem to punch them rather than draw their bows and shoot arrows. Despite this lack of proper animation, the arrows themselves can still be seen.
* The Zamorakian Spiritual rangers seem to be wearing [[Hazeel's mark]].
* Saradominist Spiritual rangers appear to be wearing the female version of [[Rogue trousers]].
* Spiritual creatures were blocked by 113,241 players and were the most blocked slayer monster in 2017{{fact}}.

